<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2014-09-17</DATELINE><TITLE>Hinokinin, an Emerging Bioactive Lignan</TITLE><BODY>Hinokinin is a lignan isolated from several plant species that has been recently investigated in order to establish its biological activities. So far, its cytotoxicity, its anti-inflammatory and antimicrobial activities have been studied. Particularly interesting is its notable anti-trypanosomal activity.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>